articles.content:
Uponreceiving the electronic patent application documents that meet the requirements set forth in the preceding Articleand are in absence of the circumstances prescribed under Paragraph 1 or 2 of Article 9, the Specific Patent Agency shall notify the user of the receipt; such notification shall contain the following:
1. the mark of the Specific Patent Agency;
2. the time of receipt of the complete electronic patent application documents;
3. the accession number or application number of the electronic patent application documentsreferred to in the preceding subparagraph; and
4. a brief summary of the electronic patent application documents received.
